<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.241102>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 10. Favosipora purpurea, holotype: 2, colony showing original color prior to bleaching; 3, autozooids, some in radiating series, and kenozooids surrounding a central brood chamber; 4, colony margin; 5, 6, short series of autozooids surrounded by kenozooids; 7, mural spines in kenozooids; 8, brood chamber; 9, 10, ooeciostome." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/241102/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

